"content": "# Jarvis 2.8 - Minimal Meta-Engine\n\n## Current Build: Compiler Core (CORE) - Bytecode & Optimization (v2.8)\n\n### Structure\n- core/framework/output.py - Basic I/O\n- core/engine/interpreter.py - SqVGr interpreter\n- core/engine/jit.py - Just-In-Time compiler\n- core/orchestrator/engine.py - Orchestrator with compiler integration\n- core/daemon/listener.py - Daemon with cache control\n- core/network/* - Distributed memory\n- core/metacontrol/* - Memory, vectorizer, optimizer, evolve\n- core/physics/* - Sensors and actuators\n- core/life/* - Autonomy, scheduler, goals\n- core/compiler/bytecode.py - SqVGr to bytecode compiler\n- core/compiler/optimizer.py - Global graph optimization\n- core/compiler/cache.py - Compilation cache\n\n### New in v2.8\n- Bytecode compilation (compact binary representation)\n- Graph-level optimizations (dead code elimination, constant folding)\n- Compilation cache with LRU eviction\n- Cache hit/miss statistics\n- Disassembler for debugging\n- CLI flag --no-cache to disable cache\n\n### Run\n\nServer:\nbash\npython run_server.py\n\n\nClient (full features):\nbash\npython run_daemon.py --sync --autonomous\n\n\nCompiler test:\nbash\npython run_compiler_test.py\n\n\n### Cache\nCache file: compiler_cache.json\nStats available via cache_stats()\n\n### Test Commands\n- сколько времени\n- случайное число\n- запиши в файл test.txt привет мир\n- скажи привет три раза"
